==旅遊==
瓦地倫原本僅有少數[[貝都因人|貝都因人]]居住，1962年電影《[[阿拉伯的勞倫斯_(電影)|阿拉伯的勞倫斯]]》為此地觀光旅遊的濫觴<ref>{{cite web |title=The Complete Guide to Lawrence's Arabia |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/travel/middle-east/the-complete-guide-to-lawrences-arabia-564189.html |website=www.independent.co.uk |publisher=''[[獨立報|The Independent]]'' |accessdate=2020-03-15 |language=en |date=2004-05-22 |archive-date=2020-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117000453/https://www.independent.co.uk/travel/middle-east/the-complete-guide-to-lawrences-arabia-564189.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，如今發達的[[旅遊業|旅遊業]]已經使得當地形成了數百人的貝都因小城，也是當地主要的收入來源，每年吸引來自世界各地的許多登山客、攀岩愛好者與旅客造訪<ref>{{cite web|last1=Sweet|first1=Joni|title=Embrace Your Inner Jasmine Glamping at Wadi Rum|url=http://www.iexplore.com/destinations/middle-east/Gamping-in-Jordan-desert-wadi-rum|website=iExplore.com|publisher=Inside-Out Media|accessdate=20 September 2016|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212020545/https://www.iexplore.com/destinations/middle-east/Gamping-in-Jordan-desert-wadi-rum|dead-url=no}}</ref>，城中帳篷和水泥住宅相互混雜。遊客需搭四輪傳動車深入沙漠風月谷，夜宿牧羊維生的[[貝都因人|貝都因人]]的帳篷裡，食用道地的烤羊排等風味餐，觀賞其傳統之精彩歌舞表演，還會受邀至貝都因人的黑色帳篷裡品嚐地道的薄荷茶及咖啡<ref>{{Cite book|title=環遊世界文化導覽|author=林高志|publisher=五南文化|year=2010|isbn=978-957-41-7344-0|location=台北市|pages=82}}</ref>。

